@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}
note over IO多路复用对比
select/poll：调用时全量遍历fd、进程挂所有fd等待队列；
epoll：ctl阶段注册fd+回调，就绪主动入就绪链表，wait只取就绪项；
底层全部复用file_operations->poll接口，靠poll_table区分实现
end note

box "用户态" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "内核三层模型对比" #LightCyan
participant SEL as "select"
participant POL as "poll"
participant EPO as "epoll(create/ctl/wait)"
end box

box "VFS底层统一" #LightGreen
participant POLL_FN as "f_op->poll(统一驱动接口)"
participant DEV_WQ as "设备等待队列"
end box

===== select流程 =====
App->SEL:select(fd_set数组,timeout)
SEL->POLL_FN:每次调用全量遍历全部fd逐个poll()
note right of SEL:fd_set定长上限，每次用户<->内核全拷贝位图
alt 无就绪
SEL->DEV_WQ:进程挂载全部fd等待队列，休眠
DEV_WQ-->SEL:任一设备就绪wake_up，唤醒后再次全量遍历所有fd
end
SEL-->App:改写fd_set，返回就绪数

===== poll流程 =====
App->POL:poll(pollfd[],nfds,timeout)
POL->POLL_FN:每次调用全量遍历数组所有fd逐个poll()
note right of POL:无fd上限，pollfd存events/revents，仍每次全拷贝数组
alt 无就绪
POL->DEV_WQ:进程挂载全部fd等待队列，休眠
DEV_WQ-->POL:任一就绪唤醒，再次全量遍历刷新revents
end
POL-->App:回填revents，返回就绪数

===== epoll流程 =====
App->EPO:epoll_create() → 创建红黑树+就绪链表rdlist
App->EPO:epoll_ctl(ADD) → 一次性调用poll注册fd+回调
note right of EPO:红黑树存监听fd，注册epoll专属回调
EPO->POLL_FN:ctl阶段仅执行1次poll，epitem挂入设备WQ
App->EPO:epoll_wait()
alt rdlist为空
EPO->EPO:进程阻塞在epoll自身等待队列
DEV_WQ-->EPO:设备就绪→回调自动把fd推入rdlist，唤醒进程
end
EPO-->App:直接拷贝rdlist就绪事件，无需全量遍历
@enduml